OL,6,FThe UN says that more than 350,000
OL,7,Fpeople have fled the city over the
OL,8,Flast week, as the situation there
OL,9,Fbecomes increasingly desperate.
OL,11,FThat means only around a quarter of
OL,12,FRafah's population have managed to
OL,13,Fescape in the last seven days since
OL,14,Fthe ground offensive began.
OL,16,F'People in absolute desperation now
OL,17,Fare taking food from the few convoys
OL,18,Fgetting through'
