OL,6,FNGO Medical Aid for Palestinians
OL,7,Freported on Monday that hospitals in
OL,8,FGaza are reporting they will only
OL,9,Ffunction for a matter of hours due to
OL,10,Ffuel shortages after the Israeli
OL,11,Fmilitary closed the Rafah crossing.
OL,13,FVery little aid has entered Rafah over
OL,14,Fthe last week as a result of Israel's
OL,15,Factions. The European Hospital has
OL,16,Falready run out of fuel and can no
OL,17,Flonger keep the lights on.
