OL,3,C'Catastrophe on catastrophe': British
OL,4,Cdoctor describes desperation in Rafah
OL,6,FDr James Smith, an emergency doctor in
OL,7,FRafah, has told ITV News about the
OL,8,Fcritical shortage of fuel and
OL,9,Fdescribed the situation around him as
OL,10,Fthe worst he has seen in his lifetime.
OL,12,FHe said: "The situation here in Rafah
OL,13,Fis catastrophic, almost beyond
OL,14,Fcomprehension. When people say all
OL,15,Feyes on Rafah, what they mean is don't
OL,16,Fturn away.
OL,18,F"This is catastrophe on catastrophe on
OL,19,Fcatastrophe, I've never seen or heard
OL,20,Fanything like it in my entire life,"
OL,21,Fhe added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/9
