OL,6,FSmith said some people are fleeing
OL,7,Fback to the southern city of Khan
OL,8,FYounis where "people are pitching up
OL,9,Ftheir tents amidst the rubble of
OL,10,Fdestroyed homes, destroyed schools and
OL,11,Fdestroyed mosques."
OL,13,F"Some organisations are doing water
OL,14,Ftrucking but otherwise, there are no
OL,15,Fbasic services to sustain human life
OL,16,Fanywhere there," he said.
