OL,6,F"At present, there are efforts to
OL,7,Freopen Nasser Hospital and efforts to
OL,8,Freopen Al Amal Hospital, but the
OL,9,Ffunctionality of both of those
OL,10,Ffacilities is far, far below that,
OL,11,Fwhich is required to provide for the
OL,12,Fnumber of people that are now living
OL,13,Fin and around the area."
OL,15,FAs of Monday, the Palestinian death
OL,16,Ftoll in Gaza has soared past 35,000,
OL,17,Fthe Hamas-led Gaza Health Ministry
OL,18,Fsaid.
