OL,6,FSince they declared war in response to
OL,7,FHamas' deadly cross border attack on
OL,8,FOctober 7, which killed about 1,200
OL,9,Fpeople, Israel's Prime Minister
OL,10,FNetanyahu has said its central goal is
OL,11,Fto destroy its military capabilities.
OL,13,FIsrael says Rafah is Hamas' in Gaza.
OL,15,FThe international community has urged
OL,16,FIsrael not to go ahead with a major
OL,17,Fground assault.
